# Kamal Secrets Configuration
#
# This file shows the format for .kamal/secrets (which should NOT be committed to git).
# Copy this file to .kamal/secrets and replace the environment variable references with
# actual values from your environment.
#
# Secrets defined here are available for reference under registry/password, env/secret,
# builder/secrets, and accessories/*/env/secret in config/deploy.yml.
#
# IMPORTANT: DO NOT ENTER RAW CREDENTIALS HERE! Pull from ENV or password manager.
# This file needs to be safe for git (use the -example suffix for the committed version).

# GitHub Personal Access Token for container registry (ghcr.io) access
# Generate at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Required scopes: read:packages, write:packages, delete:packages (optional)
GITHUB_TOKEN=$GITHUB_TOKEN
